I'm a strong supporter of the Snyder Cut because the Justice League we all watched in theaters was nowhere close to the Justice League we were promised and shown in the trailers.
I wanna say this though. No matter what your opinion is of the movie, I think we all can agree that the Snyder Cut will be far superior then what WB and Whedon gave us. I mean, even if we get the Snyder Cut and it's not this super great film we all hope and think it is, I think we all know it will be far better then the dumb watered film we got. Plus, I'm confident that the Snyder Cut will actually be a very very good comic book film. Hopefully it is indeed coming and we all get to finally see it for ourselves and we get to judge if its worthy or not
